environment:
install Anaconda3-2019.03-Linux-x86_64.sh (the newer one has a bug)
The deployment directory has cdi project, lib directory containing arrayfire and libconfig libraries, and pylibconfig2 and gputil directories.
from the deployment directory:
1. conda config --remove channels conda-forge
2. conda-build pylibconfig2
3. conda-build gputil
4. cd cdi
5. python setup.py build_ext --inplace
6. rm -rf build/
7. conda build -c conda-forge -c defaults .

to check the build locally
8. conda config --add channels conda-forge
9. conda install --use-local reccdi

to upload
10. anaconda login
11. conda upload ~/anaconda3/conda-bld/linux-64/reccdixxx
